Date: 0/0/1981
Source: Loughnan Glossary
Author: LOUGHNAN
Vol / Page: 77
Edition:
Quote: stand on: a dog at work should never turn his tail towards his sheep but should always stand on. If he turns tail they are, if only technically, not under his control.
